{
  "texts": [
    "This finding suggests that EmoKbGAN effectively integrates the context and pertinent knowledge base, leading to more varied responses.",
    "When only the generator portion of the model is used, they saw an increase in PPL scores and a fall in BLEU scores, illustrating the potency of our attribute-specific discriminators in the design.",
    "Although the suggested EmoKbGAN performs similarly to KbGAN and EmoGAN for the distinct metric, it significantly outperforms them for the BLEU and PPL measures.",
    "This proves that the model can provide more linguistically correct responses than before when attribute-specific discriminators are used jointly.",
    "When compared to the EmoKbGAN model, they also noticed a decline in the scores of the EmoKbGAN-SD and EmoKbGAN-PD models."
  ]
}